snippet.title: DEADBOLT – Launch Trailer | PS4, PS Vita
snippet.description: DEADBOLT releases February 20th! From the creators of Risk of Rain comes DEADBOLT, an extremely challenging stealth-action hybrid that allows you to take control of the reaper to quell the recent undead uprising.
